# Assets Directory

This directory holds media assets for the Cielo project:

- demo.gif — Demo recording for README
- logo.svg — Cielo logo (optional)
- architecture.png — Architecture diagram (optional)

## Recording Demo

See docs/DEMO-SCRIPT.md for instructions on recording the demo GIF.

## Recommended Tools

- asciinema + svg-term — For terminal recordings
- terminalizer — Alternative GIF recorder
- LICEcap — Simple screen capture to GIF
